  "2026-04-25T21:36:48.864Z",codex-agent,"Progress: added telemetry settings defaults/schema (enabled by default, capture_level=max, retention_days=365), config key telemetry-tracking (enabled|disabled), and first-run TTY consent prompt that persists global decision without affecting non-interactive/json/CI runs. Verification: pnpm build passed."
  "2026-04-25T21:41:03.674Z",codex-agent,"Progress: implemented telemetry runtime pipeline with command_start/command_finish events, key/value scrubbing for sensitive fields, pseudonymous installation/session identifiers, local JSONL queueing under global runtime path, retry backoff, and batched HTTPS exporter flush. Smoke checks in temporary PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH confirmed queue population and install_id persistence."
  "2026-04-25T21:49:21.975Z",codex-agent,"Verification evidence: node scripts/run-tests.mjs test -- tests/unit/config-command.spec.ts tests/unit/settings-store.spec.ts tests/unit/telemetry-runtime.spec.ts tests/unit/telemetry-consent.spec.ts tests/integration/cli.integration.spec.ts passed (5 files, 99 tests). ReadLints reports no new diagnostics on changed source/test files."
  "2026-04-25T21:59:52.236Z",codex-agent,"Remote deployment evidence ([redacted_host]): docker compose stack launched in /home/steve/container/pm-cli with telemetry-api, telemetry-worker, RabbitMQ, Postgres, Prometheus, Loki, Tempo, Alloy, Grafana and persistent volumes. Smoke validation: POST /v1/events accepted synthetic event; Postgres telemetry_events count=1 and telemetry_command_daily updated for command list-open."
  "2026-04-25T22:02:24.648Z",codex-agent,"Caddy domain wiring complete on [redacted_host]: added pm.unbrained.dev -> http://[redacted_host]:13000 and pm-cli.unbrained.dev -> http://[redacted_host]:18080 in /home/steve/caddy/npm_proxy_hosts_extracted.json, executed ./scripts/generate-validate-reload.sh, and verified both local SNI checks (--resolve to 127.0.0.1) and public HTTPS responses for /api/health and /healthz."
  "2026-04-25T22:08:00.929Z",codex-agent,"Backup/restore implemented on remote host: scripts/backup-all.sh captures Postgres dumps, RabbitMQ definitions + volume, Loki/Tempo/Grafana/Prometheus volume archives, and config tarballs with SHA256 manifest; scripts/restore-postgres.sh, restore-rabbitmq-definitions.sh, restore-volume.sh, and restore-drill.sh added. Automation: cron installed (daily backup 03:15, weekly restore drill Sunday 03:45). Validation: backup-all.sh succeeded, restore-drill.sh succeeded (telemetry_events=13, telemetry_command_daily=4), and RabbitMQ definitions restore test passed."
  "2026-04-25T22:11:46.845Z",codex-agent,"E2E validation complete using temporary project root /tmp/tmp.5CucGC9iAM (PM_PATH/PM_GLOBAL_PATH sandbox). Executed init/create/list-open/get/close via node dist/cli.js; remote evidence: telemetry_events row count increased from 24 to 34 (+10), recent commands recorded start+finish events for init/create/list-open/get/close, RabbitMQ queue pm.telemetry.events drained to 0 ready/0 unacked, Prometheus pm_telemetry_ingested_events_total increased to 11, Loki query for container=pm-telemetry-api with '/v1/events' returned 10 log lines, and Tempo spans metric tempo_distributor_spans_received_total increased to 74."
